{"tid":417913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋節月餅捐贈活動","createTime":"2017-09-29T06:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T10:02:50.000Z","uid":18948,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6d5a1bcf3779608ee34ac78cdf679144d48e41","tid":417913,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:23:00.000Z","msg":"致各連登仔：<br />\n<br />\n近年來，市民愈來愈關注「惜物、減廢」。善用社區的食物資源，推行食物回收計劃把仍可食用的食物收集起來，再分派給有需要的人士，既可解決他們的膳食問題，又可減少浪費食物。<br />\n<br />\n支持惜食香港運動，我們每人都可以出一分力。適逢中秋佳節，大家可捐出過剩的月餅予各區有需要之團體及基層家庭。詳情請參閱由惜食香港運動秘書處最新公布的「接受捐贈月餅機構名單(2017)」。<br />\n<br />\n[(See attached file: 捐贈月餅機構名單 2017.pdf)]<br />\n<br />\n請大家攜手，過一個沒有剩食的中秋！欲知更多有關惜食香港運動的資訊，可瀏覽惜食香港運動秘書處的網站(<a href=\"http://www.foodwisehk.gov.hk/zh-hk/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodwisehk.gov.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Findex.php&d=hz2uHQdD25P5LPti95DZtJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=25f16f00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.foodwisehk.gov.hk/zh-hk/index.php</a>)。<br />\n<br />\n2017年9月29日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/142133_3de9dda05c0690da414549afa0353fad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F142133_3de9dda05c0690da414549afa0353fad.jpg&h=33487043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/29/142143_ea1ae51105d1c7e06eb251a47cb0b304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F142143_ea1ae51105d1c7e06eb251a47cb0b304.jpg&h=40c361d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51a51df962c81bef39fcb4bcd12b92ad0f17edc5","tid":417913,"uid":36366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b34698c7c2e509ecfce1d22bb8