\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ececcae6fe8f611b13659c3a6c040dfd3c8cc2","tid":417913,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"我一定唔會捐俾耶教機構"},{"pid":"b8407afabca84236a019959f53c9ea4a87aaff0e","tid":417913,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一定唔會捐俾耶教機構</blockquote><br />\n你可以選擇不同的捐贈團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd9b4b7a3ba4bbd63f49375a4ecf73b30d14a8c","tid":417913,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:28:28.000Z","msg":"比廢老 食到佢地中風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2faf95b744a55f9dcb6b1591240ba5d5d480b48e","tid":417913,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不浪費食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1b5729918b516a074dffe22e414cc7932ad9ee","tid":417913,"uid":37525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"乜嘢浪費食物<br />\n月餅由整出嚟嗰下已經浪費食材<br />\n過時傳統，肥膩唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家食物豐富，仲整到手掌咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊時無好嘢食，先過時過節食下肥滯/甜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且月餅係咪只可中秋食？<br />\n放雪櫃可keep好耐，中秋過後唔食得？<br />\n中秋掉月餅除非發霉<br />\n但發霉係儲存不當，戇鳩鳩唔放雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n惜食應該源頭開始<br />\n一個月餅肥膩，一盒仲要四大個<br />\n單隻送禮又話唔好睇，要體面<br />\n過節傳統要虛偽送禮，買親就一盒<br />\n但買嚟唔係食，傳統口味已不合現代<br />\n買嚟純粹儀式，交接、送禮、完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基層無得食咪無得食<br />\n為何中秋一定要有月餅？<br />\n以前視為祭品，就話必需<br />\n但而家仲有人祭？<br />\n將高油、高熱量、高膽固醇食物送比人<br />\n係一種祝福？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c21e3c13c6306d2b448a881a90abec2140c82a0","tid":417913,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜嘢浪費食物<br />\n月餅由整出嚟嗰下已經浪費食材<br />\n過時傳統，肥膩唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家食物豐富，仲整到手掌咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊時無好嘢食，先過時過節食下肥滯/甜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且月餅係咪只可中秋食？<br />\n放雪櫃可keep好耐，中秋過後唔食得？<br />\n中秋掉月餅除非發霉<br />\n但發霉係儲存不當，戇鳩鳩唔放雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n惜食應該源頭開始<br />\n一個月餅肥膩，一盒仲要四大個<br />\n單隻送禮又話唔好睇，要體面<br />\n過節傳統要虛偽送禮，買親就一盒<br />\n但買嚟唔係食，傳統口味已不合現代<br />\n買嚟純粹儀式，交接、送禮、完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基層無得食咪無得食<br />\n為何中秋一定要有月餅？<br />\n以前視為祭品，就話必需<br />\n但而家仲有人祭？<br />\n將高油、高熱量、高膽固醇食物送比人<br />\n係一種祝福？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae524f09f3911013d13487f2dd99b2851f3ceac","tid":417913,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜嘢浪費食物<br />\n月餅由整出嚟嗰下已經浪費食材<br />\n過時傳統，肥膩唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家食物豐富，仲整到手掌咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊時無好嘢食，先過時過節食下肥滯/甜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且月餅係咪只可中秋食？<br />\n放雪櫃可keep好耐，中秋過後唔食得？<br />\n中秋掉月餅除非發霉<br />\n但發霉係儲存不當，戇鳩鳩唔放雪櫃<img src